stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Prospect
    Prospect --> Pitched: sample sent
    Pitched --> Suppressed: no / bounce
    Pitched --> Interested: yes
    Pitched --> [*]: timeout silent
    Interested --> CheckoutPending: checkout email sent
    CheckoutPending --> Active: stripe success
    CheckoutPending --> Abandoned: 7d no checkout
    Abandoned --> [*]
    Active --> PreviewPending: preview sent
    PreviewPending --> Active: approved or silent
    Active --> Paused: pause
    Paused --> Active: resume
    Active --> Drifting: no access 14d
    Drifting --> Active: access resumed
    Drifting --> Disengaged: no access 30d
    Disengaged --> Active: access resumed
    Active --> Churned: stop or cancel
    Disengaged --> Churned: billing fail
    Churned --> [*]
